#: art_admin_slemicro_podman.xml:537
#, no-c-format
msgid "&prompt.root;podman commit <replaceable>[OPTIONS]</replaceable> <replaceable>CONTAINER</replaceable> <replaceable>IMAGE</replaceable>"
